review_text:
Life on campus can be an exciting and fulfilling experience. Here is a rundown of social life, clubs, and infrastructure on a typical college campus;
Social life; - The social life on campus is an essential aspect of college life. Students get to meet new people, make friends, and develop lifelong relationships. My college has social events, parties, and cultural activities that bring students together.The companies that visit a college for placements include Microsoft Amazon Deloitte TCS Infosys and Accenture. 
The salary packages offered to students can range from 8 to 12 lakhs. The percentage of students getting placements in a college is 90 per cent.

